title: Episode 89 - Sami Jo Small Interview
itunes:title: Episode 89 - Sami Jo Small Interview
description: We're back with an another Olympian interview as we chat with three-time Olympic ice hockey player and winner of two golds and a silver medal Sami Jo Small about her amazing career, her amazing book, her love of TV shows (that Ben apparently gets way too excited to chat to her about) and just why she is always willing to ride the squirrel bike.
